WEBVTT

00:00.916 --> 00:07.238
ï»¿One of you is about to become our new Miss Universe.

00:07.747 --> 00:11.086
If for any reason she is unable to fulfill her duties,...

00:11.200 --> 00:13.476
...the first runner-up will take her place.

00:14.007 --> 00:15.561
Good luck to both of you.

00:16.796 --> 00:26.641
Miss Universe 2015 is Colombia!

00:39.794 --> 00:40.583
Okay, folks.

00:48.095 --> 00:49.518
I have to apologize.

00:51.185 --> 00:55.781
The first runner-up is Colombia.

01:00.703 --> 01:06.863
Miss Universe 2015 is Philippines.

01:11.677 --> 01:15.060
Listen folks, let me just take control of this.

01:16.369 --> 01:19.675
This is exactly what's on the card.

01:20.480 --> 01:22.833
I will take responsibility for this.

01:23.499 --> 01:24.743
It was my mistake.

01:25.159 --> 01:26.605
It was on the card.

01:27.253 --> 01:29.609
Horrible mistake, but the right thing,...

01:29.757 --> 01:31.614
...I can show it to you right here.

01:32.450 --> 01:34.739
The first runner-up is Colombia.

01:34.881 --> 01:35.801
It is my mistake.

01:36.428 --> 01:37.607
Still a great night.

01:39.272 --> 01:41.090
Please don't hold it against the ladies.

01:41.463 --> 01:42.149
Please don't.

01:42.514 --> 01:45.141
We feel so badly, but it's still a great night.

01:45.334 --> 01:46.062
Thank you all.

